    "content": [
        {
            "template": "grid", 
            "options": {
                "class": "module-full-text",
                "columns": [
                    {
                        "width": "100%",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "template": "title", 
                                "options": {
                                    "text": "Back-to-School Hub Live June 6",
                                    "style": "padding-bottom: 20px;"
                                }
                            },
                            {   
                                "template": "content",
                                "options": {
                                    "text": "
                                    We hope you are ready for a great summer! 

                                    <br>
                                    <br>
                                    Our annual Back-to-School Hub will be opening on the parent and student portals on Monday, June 6. It contains all of the forms and information you need for the coming school year, such as supply lists, uniform/dress requirements, health and travel forms, required student summer reading, and much more, specific to your division.
                                    <br /><br />
                                    When you arrive at the hub page you’ll see a Step 1, “Read this first for important information.” Read that first! (It includes dates and important notes from your division head.)
                                    <br /><br />

                                    New to the hub this year:"
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "template": "list",
                                "options": {
                                    "type": "unordered", // default, ordered, unordered, unstyled
                                    "items": [
                                        "Streamlined landing page with easy steps to follow to see all your necessary forms and fliers",
                                        "All health forms are now online at the Magnus site; we link to it from the hub",
                                        "Harker Class Trip Planner: see all class trips listed in one place for efficient planning"
                                    ]
                                }
                            },
                            {   
                                "template": "subheader",
                                "options": {
                                    "text": "Contact Info Updates"
                                }
                            },
                            {   
                                "template": "content",
                                "options": {
                                    "text": "We also want to remind you to review and update your contact information in the “Family & Student Info” section of the Parent Portal. This information will also be used for our urgent text communication system."
                                }
                            },
                            {   
                                "template": "subheader",
                                "options": {
                                    "text": "Uniform Sale Starting Tomorrow"
                                }
                            },
                            {   
                                "template": "content",
                                "options": {
                                    "text": "Lower and middle school parents, you’ll want to know that our uniform supplier, Merry Mart, will be having an Early Bird Sale June 1-7, where you can save 20% on uniform purchases using coupon code <strong>HARKER2016</strong>."
                                }
                            },
                            {   
                                "template": "subheader",
                                "options": {
                                    "text": "Textbooks"
                                }
                            },
                            {   
                                "template": "content",
                                "options": {
                                    "text": "We sent an email on May 10 detailing textbook information. If you didn’t receive that or would like to review it, you may find it on our resources tool."
                                }
                            },
                            {   
                                "template": "button",
                                "options": {
                                    "type": "primary", // primary, secondary, outline
                                    "text": "Resources",
                                    "href": "http://resources.harker.org/textbook-buy-back-and-purchase-information/"
                                }
                            },
                            {   
                                "template": "subheader",
                                "options": {
                                    "text": "Some Key Dates"
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "template": "list",
                                "options": {
                                    "type": "unordered", // default, ordered, unordered, unstyled
                                    "items": [
                                        "<strong>Mon., June 6:</strong> Back-to-School Hub opens",
                                        "<strong>Wed., July 6:</strong> Middle and upper school booklist posted in Hub and virtual bookstore opens (MBS Direct)",
                                        "<strong>Fri., July 29:</strong> 2016-17 school year forms due",
                                        "<strong>Wed., Aug. 10:</strong> Lower and middle school BEST after-school sign-up information posted (You will be getting a reminder email closer to this date.) "
                                    ]
                                }
                            },
                            {   
                                "template": "content",
                                "options": {
                                    "text": "We hope you enjoy this one-stop-shop for all your fall 2016 needs, and we wish you a safe, fun and relaxing summer. 
                                    <br /><br />
                                    Harker Office of Communication"
                                }
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        }
    ]

